      "source_text": "We review our welfare package to employees on a regular basis. During the Reporting Year, we have ",
      "unit_id": "733ff4741c456a0662664a8697cd1589f9dd03bfd5fda960e27a60c26e223e58"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-f285f0e7f0453194",
      "source_text": "offered different kinds of paid leave to eligible employees, including but not limited to the following, ",
      "unit_id": "ee00861679030df28c68fb9e6744ec992d4fdf555a0b0a16ef402fbd8febb1f3"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-f285f0e7f0453194",
      "source_text": "of which “Happy in Life” Vacation Leaves (including Children’s Graduation Leave, Children’s Wedding ",
      "unit_id": "b4532ec2e650d383eeb4d47066b83ac314d16a3eff2d8f37cf74fad370bf023a"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-f285f0e7f0453194",
      "source_text": "Paid Birthday Leave",
      "unit_id": "70a614d455339485c76310f611fb056e84f4dd0d5ceee2059930ad1a16cea4fb"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-8d344efa4b5efde5",
      "source_text": "Birthday is a key milestone in a person’s life. For this reason, birthday leave is granted ",
      "unit_id": "b76f5924f763310aa2b44db299f96ab6ca75b19af1c00d934e351b39ea3c91d0"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-4e9a51dce9c24b33",
      "source_text": "Paid Volunteer Leave",
      "unit_id": "aaa69a9a30d9b9716028630fb4858f4b42a9e24d6830521b404b0cd745f2a03e"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-adca6e6ede26ff8f",
      "source_text": "We deeply understand the importance of giving back to the society.  Therefore, we ",
      "unit_id": "e7d2ac1fc33ee01be1e7b3b27aaa049a8b33fc5cf3943ff111523569163cf2dc"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-adca6e6ede26ff8f",
      "source_text": "encourage our employees to actively take part in community services so as to ",
      "unit_id": "3fedee407ae88d76a5923c83f65ae9135989c6959dbc794c57f438be357ae2f6"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-adca6e6ede26ff8f",
      "source_text": "Actions always speak louder than words.  That’s why we offer our employees paid ",
      "unit_id": "a7b1dcc25cf0a1022507619abd9b309bbcfa3ed130a46fa1a462e8ab26071efd"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-adca6e6ede26ff8f",
      "source_text": "volunteer leaves, as a means of motivating them to participate in voluntary work.",
      "unit_id": "d0fca4c2f7854d64e9c869825e1dce911ed564177e66ff26f305cab5ff2ab1af"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-ecbc55eb10f5b3b1",
      "source_text": "5-day Full-paid Paternity Leave",
      "unit_id": "e88abb485f567b9e4c32c432e9c2ba3259c469421e6f27cf66522d1c01dee12b"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-408aba43a613f426",
      "source_text": "Since March 2013, we already granted a 5-day full-paid paternity leave to all of our ",
      "unit_id": "6fab777c86f17c428188b178096269bc307c470723430f8432f9a0bdd8acfac4"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-408aba43a613f426",
      "source_text": "eligible employees.  This is better than the statutory 5-day paternity leave which is ",
      "unit_id": "086aed99d43a269e8c673d60a30744f29b0be46dddb3f3f9f63b14be12bd46af"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-3e33ce415c667e02",
      "source_text": "Marriage Leave",
      "unit_id": "8190d8703296cd2d68990eb3e040bbe66b4832f2cd2cc2bace3086a040ee1dac"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-ed63e3bb1b0e2099",
      "source_text": "To express the Company's support towards an employee's recent marriage and allow ",
      "unit_id": "fd39a901b0ceb62e137409f577e88530d46db8adfa3be3dede66be2575b163ac"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-ed63e3bb1b0e2099",
      "source_text": "them to fully focus on this signiﬁcant milestone in their life and enjoy the happiness of ",
      "unit_id": "0769caf2b5da3af4128f5e3184af1b3eac7768cdb49ad652453ff8e38622ce7b"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-ed63e3bb1b0e2099",
      "source_text": "newlywed bliss. We granted 10 days marriage leave to all of our eligible employees.",
      "unit_id": "241d83d88ac364a3cdfeecb03da613145d469fdfb02ab7535c1ed8c9a2aa4b48"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-8bb4eccca5f7f07f",
      "source_text": "Work Anniversary Leave",
      "unit_id": "509502b857e7d11e99a84e2525159afefcacd689bfdaa30815b42ce2ba4f2659"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-d21aad1847a11683",
      "source_text": "Thank you to the employees who have grown together with the company. We ",
      "unit_id": "ef1a60c32b7d05e86b50df44efe25885e5d5e4d04fc25fbd1ec8d529c53edab0"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-d21aad1847a11683",
      "source_text": "appreciate having employees along the way, and let's celebrate your work ",
      "unit_id": "ccdde3301cd5065ef77a768cb825a0c872bb921531c1d088c830f87731f5f7d1"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-d21aad1847a11683",
      "source_text": "anniversary together. We granted 1 day work anniversary leave to those who ",
      "unit_id": "ac9fc676a5ae4b7aab3074a01dc82817a494f4eb45991c443bf697815ff2d81d"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-58518b47419e6049",
      "source_text": "complete 1 year working period at the ofﬁce.",
      "unit_id": "50e329fee13199485f82cbf995480b7aeda79f9c7f6108f5b663f471c3e0c6f5"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-58518b47419e6049",
      "source_text": "Exam Leave",
      "unit_id": "6ed99b859af5face8bbc28a16b0714b5fd70bc08a82c5e03882a28329f954436"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-24ab75332b5b72ae",
      "source_text": "Encourage employees to continuously pursue further education and enhance ",
      "unit_id": "b3d8359d7aa383abe940f288c6528576d82b7c269724ab36f073f05131e3da9f"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-24ab75332b5b72ae",
      "source_text": "themselves in order to improve their current job skills or to prepare for of new ",
      "unit_id": "cd96a49ea6b1029baf93d8ef9a4b4a0283156cfb484321116a91a2e14d1b6ec0"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 25,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-24ab75332b5b72ae",
      "source_text": "responsibilities. We granted 3 days exam leave to all of our eligible employees.",
      "unit_id": "5d7ea509c4e1bee8ee0b2f682ef1f85457d0403648d8cd4279e8b2ffc4d267bf"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 26,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-253369f069530814",
      "source_text": "\"Happy in Life\" Vacation Leave\"",
      "unit_id": "82452e96ac99439ea43f797a43129803a5fc00db13defe943132bab9ba340a61"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 27,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-5a196dd9dc802907",
      "source_text": "Promote a family-friendly work environment so that colleagues can share happy ",
      "unit_id": "19cc368d96d1d3625b79cac2271b75e9830f865ac6ff1bab7149f8e5a2e06bd0"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 28,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-5a196dd9dc802907",
      "source_text": "moments in every important milestone during their children’s life stages. We granted ",
      "unit_id": "0db33767b7ad530b9a958144ce5d15f4caf07a55fb522cb821a9e329ffc172ba"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 29,
      "page_no": 1,
      "region_id": "anchored-owner-253369f069530814",
      "source_text": "4 days vacation leave to all of our eligible employees.",
      "unit_id": "178d055d9db47131b62d9e88e53515390e2ef83b51a54b7f3c8a259b8bc4c8e8"
    },
    {
      "ordinal": 30,
      "page_no": 1,
